highlights.text: EM XINH "SAY HI" has the most spots on Top Songs Vietnam. “GÃ SĂN CÁ” is the highest at #5.
“Âm Thầm Bên Em” by Sơn Tùng M-TP has been on Top Songs Vietnam the longest, at 1686 days straight.
“DÁN MẮT” by JSOL is the highest new entry on Top Songs Vietnam at #172.
“Chấm Hết” by Dangrangto, ZEXZEX, and DONAL is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Vietnam, up 109 spots at #83.
